This is a homebrew game for the Neo Geo Pocket Color. It is not affiliated
with, endorsed by, or connected to SNK Corporation, Atari, or any other
company. "Neo Geo Pocket" is a trademark of SNK Corporation.

The game is inspired by the classic 1979 Atari Asteroids arcade game by
Ed Logg and Lyle Rains.

The ameliandev NGPC framework (library.c/h, system.lib) is used under its
original terms. The Toshiba TLCS-900H toolchain is proprietary and not
included in this repository.
